Now where was I. Cutie entered the area that would later be Augusta 
Georgia (I don't want you to know exactly where I live now do I). He 
then laid down clutching a small disk close to his heart. It showed a 
press conference with Optimus Prime after they arrived back on 
Cybertron. He didn't care his shuttle had crashed. This was the right 
planet, he had been going for the 20th-21st century but when didn't 
matter. Optimus had spoken for 4 mega cycles. He mentioned several 
Earth legends. Among them was the fountain of youth. After finding the 
disk Cutie had worked for 10 stellar cycles to find out where Earth 
was. Now he could find the fountain of youth (one of the few known 
legends with no known root in true history or nature) and pray it 
worked on bots.

OOC: If you want to complain cutties stupid talk to whoever came up 
with Bob first.
